# Terraform Remote State Backend (Optional)
#
# Uncomment and configure for team/multi-developer environments.
# For single-developer PoC, local state (default) is sufficient.
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. Create S3 bucket: aws s3 mb s3://YOUR-STATE-BUCKET --region ap-northeast-1
